        "created_at": "2023-06-30T16:20:25.666Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hello, I am trying to set up custom ports for each of my foundation db roles.  If I am able to set the port for each class I think that would accomplish what I am trying to do.  For example Id want to set storage port to 4501, log to 4601, resolvers to 4701, etc.  Is this possible to do with the operator?</p>\n<p>The reason for this is we have a custom metrics handler that is able to tell what each service is based on the port and it would be easier if I can do the same think in K8.</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 4,
        "updated_at": "2023-06-30T16:20:25.666Z",
