        "created_at": "2023-07-02T16:42:16.466Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"johscheuer\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"4038\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://avatars.discourse-cdn.com/v4/letter/j/f475e1/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> johscheuer:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Machine-Readable Status \u2014 FoundationDB 7.2</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Thanks for the response!  That\u2019s an option but this is the way it was done before and we are testing with kubernetes right now so was just seeing if there was a way I could just make it work straight off the bat.</p>",
